                        <p dir="ltr">On this ____ day of 2024, this Agreement was made and entered into by and between</p>

                        <p dir="ltr">1. Al Iskan Al Tullabi S.A.O.C (The Myriad Muscat), address Al Seeb, Al Khoud,&nbsp; P.O Box: 3288, Postal Code: 130, Sultanate of Oman (hereinafter referred to as the First Party/the Project Manager); and &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;. Address: P.O Box _____ Postal Code _____Tel: ____________&nbsp;</p>

