                    <ol>
                        <li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>Al Iskan Al Tullabi S.A.O.C <span style="color:black">(The Myriad Muscat)</span></strong>, address Al Seeb, Al Khoud, P.O Box: 3288, Postal Code: 130, Sultanate of Oman (hereinafter referred to as the <strong>First Party/the Project Manager</strong>); and &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;. Address: P.O Box _____ Postal Code _____Tel: ____________ </span></span></li>
