                    <p style="margin-left:23px; margin-right:8px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">First Party may terminate this Agreement pursuant to a notification remitted to the Second Party in the following cases: </span></span></p>

