                    <p style="margin-left:23px; margin-right:8px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">This Agreement may be terminated by either party by providing the other party a written notice of the anticipated termination date and cancellation form. In the event of early termination, the Second Party shall be liable for any outstanding rent up to the termination date. If the cancellation request is approved, the Second Party will be charged the difference in rate to cover the standard price based on the number of months stayed. The cancellation charges shall be determined based on the period stayed to match standard rates as per rate card.</span></span></p>

                    <p style="margin-left:23px; margin-right:8px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="color:#0d0d0d">In the event of an early checkout, one-month advance rent should be paid, and Security Deposit will not be refunded.</span></span></span></span></p>

