                    <p style="margin-left:23px; margin-right:8px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Upon expiry of the Agreement, the Beneficiary shall hand over the room and return all relevant keys, access cards, etc to the First Party at the end of the Agreement term in the manner it was received and remove all personal belongings from the Property. The Beneficiary shall be responsible for repairing any damage as a result of misuse or loss. This shall include, amongst other, cleaning, repairing broken fixtures &amp; fittings and repainting - as deemed necessary. </span></span></p>

                    <p style="margin-left:23px; margin-right:8px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">First Party may dispose of Second Party&rsquo;s belongings/property as Second Party&rsquo;s agent and Second Party will hold the First Party harmless from all liabilities, if the Second Party fails to remove any of their belongings/property within seven (7) days of the communication received from the First Party.</span></span></p>

                    <p style="margin-right:8px"><span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>Article (13):</strong></span></span></p>

                    <p style="margin-left:23px; margin-right:8px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Second Party agrees to indemnify and hold harmless the First Party and its officers, directors, employees, agents and affiliates from any claim, liability, loss, damage, cost or expense (including without limitation reasonable attorney&#39;s fees) arising out of use of personal belongings (tangible or intangible) or related to Second Party&rsquo;s use of the amenities offered within The Myriad Muscat or loss of data or any materials downloaded or uploaded through the service, any actions taken by the First Party in connection with the Second Party&rsquo;s use of the service, any violation of any third party&#39;s rights or a violation of law or regulation, or any breach of this Agreement.</span></span></p>

                    <p style="margin-left:5px"><span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>Article (14):</strong></span></span></p>

                    <p style="margin-left:23px; margin-right:6px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">First Party will collect, hold and process data relating to the personal data in order to meet its obligations under this Agreement in accordance with data protection laws and our privacy notice. Second Party hereby authorises the First Party to disclose Second Party&rsquo;s personal data to authorities, universities, guarantors, family members and specified third parties. First Party reserve the right to disclose Second Party personal data to assist in the prevention of crime or to protect the vital interests.</span></span></p>

                    <p style="margin-left:5px; margin-right:8px"><span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>Article (15): </strong></span></span></p>

                    <p style="margin-left:23px; margin-right:8px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">All official notifications sent by the first party will be through a WhatsApp group on the link <a href="https://chat.whatsapp.com/HVN3dy8BvqaFcLHCwzJM9f" style="color:blue; text-decoration:underline">https://chat.whatsapp.com/HVN3dy8BvqaFcLHCwzJM9f</a> , It is essential for second party to join this group in order to receive all notifications. First party cannot be held responsible if the second party is not aware of notifications sent via this channel. Additionally, there are hotlines available in the compound, and the Second Party is allowed to contact the appropriate lines when needed.</span></span></p>

                    <p style="margin-left:23px; margin-right:8px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Notices shall be sent to both parties as per the addresses set out herein.</span></span></p>

                    <p style="margin-left:5px; margin-right:8px"><span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>Article (16):</strong></span></span></p>

                    <p style="margin-left:23px; margin-right:8px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">In the event of any dispute arising between the parties, they shall attempt to resolve it amicably. If they fail, Omani courts and laws shall be competent to settle it. </span></span></p>

                    <p style="margin-left:5px; margin-right:8px"><span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>Article (17):</strong></span></span></p>

                    <p style="margin-left:23px; margin-right:8px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">This Agreement was made in duplicate signed by both parties; each party received one copy to act thereunder.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>

                    <p style="margin-left:5px; margin-right:8px"><span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif"><strong>Article (18):</strong></span></span></p>

                    <p style="margin-left:23px; margin-right:8px; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11px"><span style="font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif">Fines may be imposed on the Second Party for various violations to ensure a safe and comfortable living environment for all residents. The Agreement may be terminated or subject to additional penalties for repeat violations. The Second Party is required to settle any imposed fine within a 7-day grace period from the day the fine was issued. Failure to pay the fine within this period will result in the deactivation of the room key and the locking of the room until the fine is paid in full. The room key will be reactivated only upon full settlement of the fine. A list of penalties is annexed to this Agreement. </span></span></p>

